<th class="fn summary" colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Hannibal, son of Hamilcar Barca</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">248–183 or 182 BC</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:HannibalTheCarthaginian.jpg" class="image" title="HannibalTheCarthaginian.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dc/HannibalTheCarthaginian.jpg/200px-HannibalTheCarthaginian.jpg" width="200" height="263" border="0" /></a><br />
A Roman marble bust of Hannibal originally found at the ancient city-state of Capua in Italy. This image may not be authentic.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1" title=""><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
