<li id="cite_note-62"><b><a href="#cite_ref-62" title="">^</a></b> Hirshson, Stanley, <i>General Patton: A Soldier's Life</i>, p. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0060009837&amp;id=xOLMGBKbjGUC&amp;pg=RA1-PA163&amp;lpg=RA1-PA163&amp;ots=hrzMyFSU4J&amp;dq=Patton,+reincarnated&amp;sig=yDrvLwGAkuXAY7BHx19sXmF4-ik" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0060009837&amp;id=xOLMGBKbjGUC&amp;pg=RA1-PA163&amp;lpg=RA1-PA163&amp;ots=hrzMyFSU4J&amp;dq=Patton,+reincarnated&amp;sig=yDrvLwGAkuXAY7BHx19sXmF4-ik" rel="nofollow">163</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-63"><b><a href="#cite_ref-63" title="">^</a></b> Carlton, James, <i>The Military Quotation Book</i>, New York City, New York, Thomas Dunne Books, 2002</li>
</ol>
